Package: pcal
Type: Package
Title: Calibration of P-Values for Point Null Hypothesis Testing
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
  person("Pedro", "Fonseca", email = "pedro.teles.fonseca@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5708-081X")),
  person("Rui", "Paulo", role = c("ctb", "ths"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5708-081X")),
  person(given = "FCT", role = "fnd"))
Description: Calibrate p-values under a robust perspective and obtain measures of 
    the evidence provided by the data in favor of point null hypotheses which are safer  
    and more straightforward to interpret, having both Bayesian and Frequentist
    interpretations.
